title: Undine
actors: Paula Beer,Franz Rogowski,Maryam Zaree,Jacob Matschenz,Anne Ratte-Polle,Rafael Stachowiak,Julia Franz Richter,Gloria Endres de Oliveira,José Barros,Enno Trebs,Christoph Zrenner,Stefan Walz,Bita Steinjan
summary: Undine works as a historian lecturing on Berlin's urban development. When the man she loves leaves her, the ancient myth catches up with her. But falling in love anew, Undine reworks the myth of the mysterious water spirit as a modern fairy-tale in a disenchanted world.

summary: In 1930’s England, a group of pretentious rich and famous gather together for a weekend of relaxation at a hunting resort. But when a murder occurs, each one of these interesting characters becomes a suspect.
